    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a dependable choice for anyone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches, some minor door dings, and the clear coat is starting to show age on the roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor stains on the carpet. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next year. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left for its next owner.",
