    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, original state with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. It has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, making it a perfect find for a collector or someone seeking a like-new driving experience.",
