    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, preserved in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This vehicle has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, showing no discernible signs of previous ownership. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of uncompromising caliber, fully inspected and prepared for the most discerning enthusiast.",
